# System and versions
I tried following setups:
* PC with Intel Core i7-4790, 16GB RAM, Windows 7 Service Pack 1.
Visual Studio 2012 x64 + dlib 18.14 / Visual Studio 2015 x64 + dlib 19.4
for server and client apps running through localhost

* Laptop with Intel Core i7, 8GB RAM, Fedora Linux Release 20 x64
gcc 4.8.3 + dlib 18.14 
for client app sending data to windows pc via ethernet connection.

In case with real ethernet connection situation reproduced on even smaller images.

## what did i come up with so far
* Adding this_thread::sleep doesn't help.
* I tried running visual studio debug for both server and client, but couldn't find anything - i went up to calls to `WaitForSingleObject`. I aslo noticed that when I am at breakpoints in both server and client, all messages miss.

I have built and installed dlib19.4 successful. 
I want to use dlib's dnn library to build cnn. 
